<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to WhatsApp CRM</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #667eea; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .features { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .feature-item { padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    .footer { text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 30px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>ðŸŽ‰ Welcome to WhatsApp CRM!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi {{tenantName}},</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for subscribing to <strong>{{planName}}</strong>! Your subscription is now active and you have access to all the features included in your plan.</p>
    
    <div class="features">
      <h3>Your Plan Features:</h3>
      {{#each features}}
      <div class="feature-item">âœ“ {{this}}</div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
    
    <p>Ready to get started? Visit your dashboard to begin managing your WhatsApp conversations, contacts, and campaigns.</p>
    
    <center>
      <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
    </center>
    
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is here to help at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>The WhatsApp CRM Team</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© 2025 WhatsApp CRM. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
